e":{"pid":"d3197daca541ddd1d4ea7582723e02541f8378a5","tid":819061,"uid":4679,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:00:33.000Z","msg":"喜歡 唔需要理由<br />\n快樂 需要理由"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:05:30.000Z","msg":"之前睇過一個解釋係<br />\n<br />\n喜= 你因為某個人/某件事而開心<br />\n樂= 自己心境保持快樂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"=樂&gt;喜?<br />\n<br />\n最大不解係 人有咁多感覺<br />\n點解要放兩個意思相關既係一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"喜同哀相對<br />\n怒同樂相對"},{"pid":"a0987026a8dd30ef150b73b190ba4f4506498267","tid":819061,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"喜係自身<br />\n樂係受人事物影響<br />\n好似bored 同boring"},{"pid":"f9637421bf04d1a5d99b36fb1f786706409c95cf","tid":819061,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"喜  由外到內 既開心<br />\n樂  由內至外 既開心"},{"pid":"bf738a760fbe6b60a33d8775752c7ac617a865f6","tid":819061,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9bafafe253ff3a2dee05182cfb47739bdc65576","tid":819061,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf738a760fbe6b60a33d8775752c7ac617a865f6","tid":819061,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0987026a8dd30ef150b73b190ba4f4506498267","tid":819061,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"喜係自身<br />\n樂係受人事物影響<br />\n好似bored 同boring"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"有無道理先"},{"pid":"17ef227d7a7b6cd11974f8e6d9a37398bf80c20c","tid":819061,"uid":91833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"3 個解答 &middot; 語言 <br />\n 最佳解答<br />\nHello 版大 fookfook3 施主 您好ㄚ！ <br />\n<br />\nQ：喜怒哀樂中的「喜」及「樂」其實有甚麼分別? <br />\nA：意思確實很相近，例如： <br />\n1. 因為喜歡他，所以跟他在一起很快樂。 <br />\n2. 他是個幽默的人，跟他在一起，讓我很快樂，所以我喜歡他。 <br />\n<br />\n個人解釋如下： <br />\n喜歡＝不需要有理由的。（我就是喜歡她的一切。） <br />\n快樂＝是有理由的。（因為某人或某件事物而高興。） <br />\n<br />\nQ：另外，亦想知道喜怒哀樂的出處? <br />\nA：用Google搜尋結果，其出處是 <br />\n《禮記．中庸》：&ldquo;喜怒哀樂之未發謂之中，發而皆中節謂知和。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\nQ：最後是為了順口?為何不以其他情緒來代替相似的喜】與【樂】，如憎恨。 <br />\nA：喜怒哀樂＝喜歡、惱怒、悲哀、快樂，用來形容人的各種不同的感情。 <br />\n<br />\n從字面上來看，喜與怒，兩字是對比的，哀與樂兩字，也是對比的。古人作詞或詩時，大多是用意思相近或相反的字來表達的。 <br />\n<br />\n◎這樣的說明可以嗎？"},{"pid":"883a1529c7a351431f681431efb2cc05605a5c55","tid":819061,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"問連登浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bca6749030d1aab89c614dd58b055888b9b2d99","tid":819061,"uid":140802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0987026a8dd30ef150b73b190ba4f4506498267","tid":819061,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"喜係自身<br />\n樂係受人事物影響<br />\n好似bored 同boring"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"I am interested in your interesting description<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n有咩係唔受人事物影響都會喜(開心?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n打丁都唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b007953ff3276dcab3b821eef0dcb1fff3a264","tid":819061,"uid":58931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fae078a768f90d58ebc4f869999abcddf6bff5a","tid":819061,"uid":208235,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"喜 = 喜呀喜呀嘻 嘻呀喜啊希"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas